snippet.textDisplay: I think some of y’all are too young to remember when this show first aired. What made KUWTK so successful at the time was the premise that they would show EVERYTHING and they DID. All three of them. But it’s true as Kim said that recently Khourtney has been sharing less and less but still getting the same amount of money as everyone else. It’s not whether she should share EVERYTHING, Kim and Khloe don’t share everything but Khourtney shares LESS than all the other girls which is why Khloe is saying that is coasting which is true. Khourtney has spent the past two seasons complaining about the family and complaining about the show yet she is the only one that does absolute ZERO about it. She hasn’t done much to build her brand outside of the show which makes her not want to quit the show even though she hates being on it! Basically she wants all the money without the sacrifice and that’s not fair to Kim or to Khloe who are the only two people worth watching this show for. Ever since the Scott drama stopped Khourtney has had no storyline and she just can’t deal. Either she gets up and does something with her life (quit the show, find something else to do) or she should do what the show requires which is to SHARE MORE. Period.
